Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================AVANT====================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.85,0:00:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子 那天…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.78,0:00:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我和你看到了一樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.06,0:00:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一樣的東西是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你是透子的什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.93,0:00:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}來這裡是為了見透子？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.11,0:00:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}「嗯」什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.72,0:00:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}為什麼你會知道這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:25.63,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\be2}CAFE 風道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這裡是你們聚會的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明天十一點 我在麒麟館的眺望台等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}等等…喂
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================A-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不用去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}為什麼由你決定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.26,0:02:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}他也真是直爽乾脆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.24,0:02:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}倒是 你跟剛才那個大衛是什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.87,0:02:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在學校談論過雞的關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那麼為什麼明天要見面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.68,0:02:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不過 他倒是個帥哥啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}和這個沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}想去見的話就去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不過 我還是覺得男人的性格比臉蛋重要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.99,0:02:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}所以說 不是那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}有什麼介意的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那麼我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.71,0:02:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}他沒說讓你一個人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那麼 大家一起去不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你還真是少根筋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.70,0:02:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不懂女人心的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}女人心是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我來告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我不是說了不要隨便進來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.33,0:03:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}還以為你叫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明顯沒叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}懂得女人心的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}既有身高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}又有經濟力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}腦子還聰明的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是能看穿這些話只是嘴上說說而已的傢伙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 集中精力 集中精力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你的碎片找到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒來得及準備房間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}本週內會盡力準備好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我很中意那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}中意在院子裡搭帳篷露營嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那麼 作為父親我就沒臉見人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}對了 我馬上要出門 所以不需要午餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}去做什麼 約會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}有點失敗 勉強修復好的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}看不出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你願意收下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}算是今天陪我的謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小幸的處女作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天來這裡 和那個一閃一閃的有關嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.53,0:06:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你是昨天的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}永宮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}永宮是擔心透子所以來這裡的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要怎麼做才能得到你的信任呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}離透子遠一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}很難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是我說 我能解決透子一部分的煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你會怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}只要有某些誘因 透子就會看到幻覺般的東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我想和沖倉同學談談
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你會幫助透子的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我在樓下等著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.86,0:06:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.01,0:07:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}對了 我們幾個是禁止戀愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我覺得這種規定 很快就會失效的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子怎麼看自己的才能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}自己的才能？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}說成能力也行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}關於你的幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}去外面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我想向透子道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}對了 那麼單方面地定約
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是我不來的話 你準備怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是那樣 無論多少次我都會去見你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天有點大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:07:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}所以聽到了透子的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那個 不太懂你的意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}毫無徵兆地 聽到了未來傳來的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我的…未來的聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你向我道歉就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我以為沒被任何人聽到的 在浴室裡唱的歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不 比起這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}難道是我念叨考試成績的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}很糟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}考試成績
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一般不會問這個的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}體諒一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你相信我了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你要是現在承認自己說謊了 我會原諒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}按照三秒規則
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}前些日子 祭典那天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我第一次看到了圖像和聲音貼合的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}碎片？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也是第一次聽到聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:08:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我聽到的未來的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我把它叫做未來的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}未來的碎片？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.93,0:09:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子看到的也是這種
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我能看到未來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}大概是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}看到幻覺般東西的時候 總有一些誘因的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}有那個的話 大概 會很容易看到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}玻璃 就可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一閃一閃的東西都可以 但是玻璃特別容易
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 就這樣 把意識集中到玻璃上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也想…看到未來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}剛才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.57,0:10:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}果然 和你在一起 我也能看到圖像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}之前從沒有看得這麼清晰過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}而且連聲音都能聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你怎麼知道這就是未來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}只能說因為我就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就像剛才那樣 兩個人在一起的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就可以既看到圖像又聽到聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}知道了這個能怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}總之先給你這個 電話號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.96,0:10:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}難道是家裡的號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}雖然知道那個人不是壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我卻無法喜歡上他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}他沒對你做什麼奇怪的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是有什麼人讓透子困擾的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我一定不會原諒他
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}已經是最後的機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}得說出口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎麼說我也是個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}噢～ 是個男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我就不說別隨便進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}作為姐姐至少要看一下氣氛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}說起來 前些日子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我看到那孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你喜歡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}住口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那孩子在醫院裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}有哪裡不舒服嗎　
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}她說是定期要去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}紅顏薄命的病弱西施嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一看就是你喜歡的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不要隨便說別人薄命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}呀 昨天見過了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我叫井美雪哉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.31,0:12:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我叫 沖倉驅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 好早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂 有好好地保持節奏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}給 喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}笨蛋 別無視我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好不容易有了好轉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要控制住保持好節奏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}還有 祐給大家傳了簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}待會去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}遇見大衛了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}大衛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 昨天的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不想輸給他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}什麼 我聽不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 怎麼了 小柳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}想和你談談心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那個 我想去告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你知道對方是誰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}說說看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小雪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你知道的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我一直覺得你們很配
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳和小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是 雪 好像有喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那一定是小柳了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你還是先做好被告白的準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎麼準備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}而且 也不知道是不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一定沒錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是失敗了的話 我就沒辦法和大家在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒有這回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}能自己堅定地做出決定 小柳好了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我會支持你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多謝 透子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂 浴室空了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}浴室？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.61,0:14:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不可能兩個人一起洗的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}被告白的準備是怎樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}準備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}噢 今天是炸雞塊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}突然想吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}雞肉買太多了 把冰箱都塞滿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}姐姐 今天去了麒麟館了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.14,0:15:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 好想涼台上也有空調
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}說到麒麟館
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那可是滿載著我們的回憶的地方呢 真理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}回想起來 二十年前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}救了因太忘我地臨摹展出來的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}屏氣太久而倒下的真理的是爸爸我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}聽不懂你在說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}被抱起醒來後的真理這麼說道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}居然能這麼快爬上樓來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}於是 我立刻回答說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是下樓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}呀 好害羞呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}媽媽 這是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}完全不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂 陽菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}如果 只是說如果哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.04,0:15:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是能預知未來的話 你想做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}突然說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:15:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}靠賽艇大賺一筆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 難道不是預知將來會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.57,0:16:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}結沒結婚這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這些才是 預先知道了就沒意思了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 至少等成年了再說吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.02,0:16:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}她說今天來不了了 拖堂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}昨天怎麼樣 小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}與前些日子那個人來這裡的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}感覺完全沒區別
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我覺得只是平常地聊了聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}「我覺得」是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}因為我不在場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你讓他們倆獨處了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}咦 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就是這樣 和簡訊上說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明天大家一起登山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}首先說明一下集合時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在那之前 我有想通知的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}請說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:17:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}戀愛 解禁了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 戀愛本來是禁止的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒錯 但是從現在開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不 不用等…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}咦 柳同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}大家已經回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這樣啊 沒想到早早結束了 所以我就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}讓我稍微休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明天的預定問雪哉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}您要點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}蘋果茶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 還有 透子同學的通知
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:17:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}戀愛 解禁了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}想起來還有事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 小雪 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.52,0:18:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}能等一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天也好熱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 抱歉 有什麼事來著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你昨天和大衛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}昨天？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 難道說已經跟你說了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}說了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}比如談談心什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}談心…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒錯 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.14,0:18:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小雪很容易害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}和女孩子面對面的時候 也許不能很溫柔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不 不對 雖然很溫柔…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.52,0:19:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}心意什麼的 不說出口來經常就會傳達不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒傳達到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}對珍重的人 說出你的真心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是呀 不說出口來不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子 我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.77,0:19:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}等等 告訴我幹什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.32,0:19:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我…喜歡…透子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喜歡透子！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多…多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}雪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}擺出一張傻子一樣的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你怎麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:20:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}什麼 在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:21:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這是我回家的路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.77,0:21:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.73,0:21:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}走 回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎麼辦 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}得做點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂 我是沖倉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那個 啊 那個 我是深水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一個學校的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.08,0:21:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 沖倉同學 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我想…看到未來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也想…看到未來
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================NEXT====================
